* chin-ma-ya.org

chin-ma-ya.org is not in use now(2009/11/02).
Instead of it, chinma-ya.appspot.com is now available.
But perl programs are disabled. So shops will not update.

http://chinma-ya.appspot.com/
http://bitbucket.org/takatoshi.ono/chinma-ya/

Perl programs may be transport to GAE apps in future :)

